io.netty.buffer

Class UnpooledUnsafeDirectByteBufWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.netty.buffer.ByteBuf
      • io.netty.buffer.AbstractByteBuf
        • io.netty.buffer.AbstractReferenceCountedByteBuf
          • io.netty.buffer.UnpooledUnsafeDirectByteBufWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.netty.util.ReferenceCounted, Comparable<ByteBuf>

    public final class UnpooledUnsafeDirectByteBufWrapper
extends AbstractReferenceCountedByteBuf
    A NIO ByteBuffer, byte[] and address direct access wrapper. Only content manipulation operations are supported. Is best suited only for encoding/decoding purposes.
